Package com.iontrading.mkv

Interface IMkvTickData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MkvE2ETickData, MkvTickData
    @Keep
@KeepPublicClassMembers
public interface IMkvTickData
    Public interface for reporting performance measurement ticks

    This interface has the following concrete implementations:

    • MkvTickData: the root structure of the hierarchy, able to store the ticks in a bucket-ordered distribution
    • MkvE2ETickData: for reporting End-to-End delays / application Round-Trip delays
    See Also:
    MkvTickData, MkvTickDataCollector
